Package: perchr
Type: Package
Title: API Wrapper for the Perch API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Luis", "Rodriguez Castellano", email = "drluisrod.perfscience@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a simple R interface to the Perch API, enabling users to
    authenticate, retrieve, and organize Perch data (e.g., sets, users, exercises)
    directly into R for analysis.
